=====================================================================
COMPANION — PARALLEL BEATS AND NEW SCENES
=====================================================================
Companion to: NEXT SESSION - forelhost finale to gate 3
Source design: LAST RIFTEN SESSION (planning), Sections II–IV
Runs alongside: §9 ORION'S BUSINESS: GRELOD / HONORHALL

These three scenes exist so the rest of the table has LIVE PLAY while
Orion infiltrates solo. They are modular — run any, all, or none as
time allows; they weave into the camp night, not a fixed order. The
Ylva → Ismara collision fits best LATE in the evening (after the cure
beat has established Ismara's register for the table).

ISMARA IS DRIVING FOR ALL OF THESE unless noted. Play her per
Npcs/Ismara: helpful, dry, never states a falsehood, care that is real
but instrumental. Short sentences when she's working; warmth in full
paragraphs. The meta lever: make her REWARDING to play.

